---
title: Spicy Turkey & White Bean Chili Verde with White Rice, Sour Cream & Cilantro
description: Get ready to be transported to a delicious happy place thanks to tonight’s riff on classic chili verde. You’ll simmer cumin- and garlic-seasoned ground turkey and hearty cannellini beans with our spicy-tangy green salsa, and serve it all over with buttery rice with a dollop of sour cream for creamy tanginess. A final flourish of fresh chopped cilantro adds herbaceous green contrast. Grab a big spoon and get comfy with this cozy, satisfying bowl of goodness.
